{
  "texts": [
    "To comment on the artistic synergies in the text creation process through GPT-3, and to discuss the human or non-human nature of the creative process.",
    "Artificial intelligence is opening doors of communication to the future that give us a glimpse at the work of future human and non-human artists.",
    "There are numerous works of electronic art that incorporate text as a base of the production and creative process, as well as works in which text forms part of the final result.",
    "In both cases, the text in its written version is one of the fundamental aspects of the creative process, and also the core part of the communication processes, in this case, between the artist, their work and the audience.",
    "GPT-3 is so powerful and sophisticated that it can emulate the information collection and processing process of the brain in a way that is so similar that the moral and ethical implications of its use are currently being studied."
  ]
}